{"tid":1416644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋豬引肉] 應 唔 應 該 讓 步「釋 出 善 意」？","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:21:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:15.000Z","uid":51171,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe9dc7907622e340ee83744f3ee8e6a2cfd02ba","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"睇埋先屌，唔同意都冇所謂，一齊討論，我係鬼嘅話我五雷轟頂不得好死。<br />\n===============================<br />\n<br />\n呢個做法嘅<strong><ins>前提</ins></strong>係，你係同意民意(=潛在動員能力)係重要嘅。target緊嘅係中間偏黃、淺黃、保守啲嘅人，唔係偽中立、勝利球迷、藍絲等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">如果有一刻，我地呢邊民意漸弱，同唔同意將五大訴求減至三大訴求</span>(詳細見下)，<strong><ins>扮向政府釋出善意(目的唔係向政府妥協，冇人想同佢deal。而係做場戲俾其他人睇)，將接下來嘅示威活動所帶來嘅責任、輿論壓力拋返俾政府。</ins></strong>(雖然呢樣我地而家都叫做到，但難免會失去)<br />\n<br />\n另一個作用係可以<strong><ins>避免他日政府扮釋出善意、答允我地上面想剔除嘅訴求(eg 撤回兩字)，到時將有大部份人收貨，壓力就去返我地到，所以先下手為強</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n五變三，心水清就知有邊幾項係真係不可剔除、有邊一兩項係可以剔除(當然唔剔除呢一兩項都會有佢嘅政治作用：展示市民決心、展示市民嘅權力大於政府)。<br />\n<br />\n三項如下：<br />\n1.成立獨立調查委員會調查警方行為失當、濫權及違法行為。<br />\n2.釋放並不追究為社會利益出發的示威人士/撤消所有暴動罪名的起訴。<br />\n3.實行真普選。<br />\n===========================<br />\n<br />\n上面講左，讓步有讓步嘅目的，唔讓步亦有唔讓步嘅作用。<br />\n<br />\n我未有答案(旨在俾個idea大家)，因為我同時亦諗起：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「中國人的性情是總喜歡調和折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就來調和，願意開窗了。」</strong>"},{"pid":"74a60b6b3597c5a36ed45a0a5cf3a6b5d89e5da9","tid":1416644,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n善意就係和平集會，連儂牆嗰啲<br />\n和理非回合<br />\nset deadline"},{"pid":"a7c1d9abfd8958a1e92d384ac7549296374dc0c5","tid":1416644,"uid":72994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"不失為一個option"},{"pid":"3613ea60eb35611b0a9a27cd2eec0e30dc993d6b","tid":1416644,"uid":80125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3aabb3456830e66f7c22a42bad2a555786e51f1a","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74a60b6b3597c5a36ed45a0a5cf3a6b5d89e5da9","tid":1416644,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"ok<br />\n善意就係和平集會，連儂牆嗰啲<br />\n和理非回合<br />\nset deadline"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:26:51.000Z","msg":"我上面講嘅「讓步」，講白啲，係俾緊後盾勇武派 in將來。"},{"pid":"8f7e97f4779b7cd75f092df9636b203c85fb71c8","tid":1416644,"uid":188978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"第一項同第二項其實道理上係有矛盾。純理性討論。"},{"pid":"f6f1f63fe034000ce81dbe755402e34cb0071cc1","tid":1416644,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"問題係依家無大台，邊個可以坐上談判枱上面同政府deal?"},{"pid":"e1c064d1b5d858b8892a8936c4c27216776d4193","tid":1416644,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察已經成為過街老鼠<br />\n下一步就要對準政權 五大訴求<br />\n要讓一班高官切身感到害怕 連記者會都唔感出黎<br />\n放？都係放高官屋企</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"82161991f69a0f0cb37c00929cdd577fbf9de175","tid":1416644,"uid":174283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:32:45.000Z","msg":"你都痴線<br />\n人民叫價叫到天咁高都得啦"},{"pid":"f0779ec899763d91f802273b0273fe1f203cec78","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f7e97f4779b7cd75f092df9636b203c85fb71c8","tid":1416644,"uid":188978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:28:36.000Z","msg":"第一項同第二項其實道理上係有矛盾。純理性討論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"我明，即係有啲雙重標準。<br />\n我咁寫嘅目的就係想「拆掉屋頂來起一扇窗」。<br />\n<br />\n如果要deal，第一項可以係(但我地不會主動提出，就好似賣餸講價咁，set個lowest price in mind)調查雙方。"},{"pid":"44eaa741bc4d7d550587eb09aa378c0b79444148","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6f1f63fe034000ce81dbe755402e34cb0071cc1","tid":1416644,"uid":36738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"問題係依家無大台，邊個可以坐上談判枱上面同政府deal?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"不需大台，網上聲明都可以，而家冇大台政府都好清楚市民嘅訴求呀。<br />\n<br />\n有大台嘅壞處係：一捉走大台，大家就會有群龍無首嘅感覺，有失敗、完結嘅感覺，不能long last。冇大台其實就係隱形大台，你知道有個大台但你拆不掉它(當然壞處就係欠效率)。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係真係真係要搵一個人出黎，可以搵民主派吧，都係做傳話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f5dbd011769b6852c3f43efd4d0eb7e90dd224","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd24aad72a2396f43c19fa9c113d9ba9031ec9a2","tid":1416644,"uid":32528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"比個位佢讓步"},{"pid":"a9cfc62f18050085299c9233b41290afe3a1f691","tid":1416644,"uid":90883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:02:18.000Z","msg":"老實講 我覺得可以考慮向警察釋出善意 認清返本來既敵人 即係港共"},{"pid":"f012f22384bd5bc9cb759ff5311413f4865e8cc9","tid":1416644,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"Okay"},{"pid":"06d5e77d4db71608fb1c235dd7b67b96474c665b","tid":1416644,"uid":260906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf155bcd58911d9906f6edb82d58873cdc604f94","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"點解要讓步?<br />\n我地做咁多野乜都得唔到就讓步?<br />\n咁仲點樣繼續爭取餘下ge野?"},{"pid":"efe1f2748b036c69618b9cfa943ef78cf18f934c","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf155bcd58911d9906f6edb82d58873cdc604f94","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"點解要讓步?<br />\n我地做咁多野乜都得唔到就讓步?<br />\n咁仲點樣繼續爭取餘下ge野?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"巴打睇左嗰兩個目的(拋返個波俾政府+先下手為強)未？讓步係為左得到想要嘅。"},{"pid":"3e54229f83c9f8cd058142aa73252775a32f9623","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe1f2748b036c69618b9cfa943ef78cf18f934c","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf155bcd58911d9906f6edb82d58873cdc604f94","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"點解要讓步?<br />\n我地做咁多野乜都得唔到就讓步?<br />\n咁仲點樣繼續爭取餘下ge野?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"巴打睇左嗰兩個目的(拋返個波俾政府+先下手為強)未？讓步係為左得到想要嘅。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n但呢個階段講讓步係不切實際<br />\n亦都唔會有人願意聽<br />\n因為呢個政府冇軟化ge跡象"},{"pid":"32cb67dbbc2b3df86a240ccf92a724644074b4c4","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e54229f83c9f8cd058142aa73252775a32f9623","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe1f2748b036c69618b9cfa943ef78cf18f934c","tid":1416644,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf155bcd58911d9906f6edb82d58873cdc604f94","tid":1416644,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:08.000Z","msg":"點解要讓步?<br />\n我地做咁多野乜都得唔到就讓步?<br />\n咁仲點樣繼續爭取餘下ge野?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"巴打睇左嗰兩個目的(拋返個波俾政府+先下手為強)未？讓步係為左得到想要嘅。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n但呢個階段講讓步係不切實際<br />\n亦都唔會有人願意聽<br />\n因為呢個政府冇軟化ge跡象"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"明白，都唔會係呢幾日做嘅事。<br />\n都係諗定黎緊民意有回落時可以點搞返著，<br />\n鞏固返個民意後盾去support個運動。<br />\n<br />\n政府方面我都知一定冇咁易，一定要靠運動去令佢收皮。而上面所講嘅「讓步」就係去加強返個民意，等市民可以繼續個運動。"}]}